--- In EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com, Frank Ratka &lt;warrior18eii@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;
&gt; LC,
&gt; 
&gt; Yeah, I have it installed on Radio #1 (the 12-469) of my scan 
array. I think it helps a lot by breaking up the patterns that can 
develop while having all three radios scanning at the same rate. If I 
didn&#39;t have radios#1 set to a slower scan rate the radio outputs were 
developing harmonics that were causing a feedback loop. I was still 
getting recordable speech but it would be drowned out in places by 
these alien tones.
&gt; 
&gt; Regards,
&gt; 
&gt; Frank R.
